hu.akarnokd.rxjava3.basetypes

Class NonoProcessor

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.akarnokd.rxjava3.basetypes.Nono
      • hu.akarnokd.rxjava3.basetypes.NonoProcessor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Processor<Void,Void>, Publisher<Void>, Subscriber<Void>

    public final class NonoProcessor
extends Nono
implements Processor<Void,Void>
    A hot Nono that signals the terminal event to Subscribers.

    NonoProcessor is thread-safe and naturally serialized on its onXXX methods.

    Since:
    0.12.0
